         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Western Postcard Collection. Yale Collection of Western Americana, Beinecke Rare Book and Manuscript Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_35a2f2fb2a459333a4bdd6ebf4ff5822">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Purchased from Thomas C. Klopp on the Arthur Corbitt Hoskins Memorial Fund, William Robertson Coe Fund No. 3, and the Frederick W. and Carrie S. Beinecke Fund for Western Americana, 2011-2014.</p>
         <p>July 1998 Acquisition: purchased from Ronald Rayman on the Arthur Corbitt Hoskins Memorial Fund.</p>
         <p>May 2009 Acquisition: purchased from Ray C. Chasteen on the Arthur Corbitt Hoskins Memorial Fund.</p>
         <p>August 2012 Acquisition: purchased from Vigilante Rare Documents on the Frederick W. and Carrie S. Beinecke Fund for Western Americana.</p>
         <p>July 2014 Acquisition: source unknown.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
